# attached_assets/: optional working-reference files (screenshots, branding notes).
# It contains working reference files (screenshots, branding uploads) shared with the agent.
# These files are NOT served by the application; production assets live in
# artifacts/accessibility-now/public/ instead. We commit attached_assets/ so the files
# are available across sessions, but large binary uploads should be avoided.
# See attached_assets/README.md for full guidance.
